Unfortunately, this contains a lot of instance names which are not in #aligns. The list of remaining declarations to track down is:

Entries in `docs/undergrad.yaml` refer to declarations that don't exist. Please correct the following:

  Ring Theory :: Ideals and Quotients :: quotient rings: ideal.has_quotient

  Ring Theory :: Divisibility in integral domains :: $\Z$ is a euclidean ring: int.euclidean_domain
  Ring Theory :: Polynomial rings :: $K[X]$ is a euclidean ring when $K$ is a field: polynomial.euclidean_domain

  Ring Theory :: Field Theory :: field $\R$ of real numbers: Real.division_ring

  Single Variable Real Analysis :: Topology of R :: completeness of R: Real.completeSpace

  Topology :: Hilbert spaces :: dual space: normed_space.dual.normed_space
  Topology :: Hilbert spaces :: inner product space $l^2$: lp.inner_product_space
